35:05.923 --> 35:08.464
-Thank you for everything.
-Susie: Bye, Carol.

35:12.506 --> 35:14.130
(door closes)

35:15.881 --> 35:17.422
Carol.

35:18.339 --> 35:20.756
-Hey, baby.
