-So all of this is fake.

35:40.673 --> 35:42.005
None of this has been real.

35:42.089 --> 35:43.631
No, no, it isn't fake,
actually, Clive.

35:43.714 --> 35:45.464
-Isn't it?
-Yes, okay, it is fake!

35:45.547 --> 35:47.506
