want to hear?
It's fake!

35:47.589 --> 35:50.214
-You-- Don't go!
-(grunts)

35:50.422 --> 35:51.881
Get-- Leave my--

35:51.964 --> 35:53.756
(engine revving)

35:56.631 --> 35:58.714
(honking)

35:58.798 --> 36:01.047
Carol, no! Carol!

36:01.130 --> 36:03.339
-(honking)
-(screams)

36:07.547 --> 36:09.547
